Text: 'What if you spent some time alone in this beautiful world,so let''s just start
  it with India.

  India is popularly known for its culture and several religion. Once you get into
  this country you will never feel alone, people get connected to you so easily and
  so perfectly . The culture of india is so fascinating and admiring too. In India
  you will get to know about assorted form of god and goddesses. Different parts of
  India have different speciality some are popular for its food were some are popular
  for its tradition and culture. The beauty of this country cannot be explained it
  is so special that you can only feel only through the part of this place.'
